{"type":"npc_class","name":"ASSASSIN","img":"systems/lancer/assets/icons/npc_class.svg","system":{"lid":"npcc_assassin","name":"ASSASSIN","role":"striker","info":{"flavor":"Assassins tend towards agility, damage, and speed. These pilots sacrifice comfort for efficiency, stripping out everything from life-support to comms systems and replacing them with increased processing power and stealth capabilities. Assassins work alone or in small groups, piloting their small, sleek mechs through near-impenetrable terrain to catch their targets off-guard.","tactics":"Assassins are true experts at punishing single characters. Use Assassin’s Mark to choose a target, and then make the most of the Assassin’s high speed and Leap to close the distance. For a nasty combination, pair an Assassin with NPCs that inflict mobility-reducing conditions like Stunned or Prone. Without optional systems like the “Devil’s Cough” Shotgun, Assassins only have access to melee attacks and are fairly vulnerable to sustained damage."},"power":100,"base_features":[{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_kai_bioplating_assassin","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_heated_blade_assassin","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_assassins_mark_assassin","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_leap_assassin","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"}],"optional_features":[{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_devils_cough_shotgun_assassin","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_sap_assassin","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_spinning_kick_assassin","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_cloud_projector_assassin","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_explosive_knives_assassin","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"}],"base_stats":{"activations":[1,1,1],"armor":[0,1,1],"hp":[15,15,15],"evade":[12,15,17],"edef":[8,8,8],"heatcap":[7,7,7],"speed":[6,6,8],"sensor":[10,10,10],"save":[10,12,14],"hull":[0,1,1],"agility":[2,3,4],"systems":[1,1,2],"engineering":[-1,0,0],"size":[[0.5,1],[0.5,1],[0.5,1]]}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"kpZ1DNCgd1F5Mepo":3},"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"lancer","systemVersion":"1.6.1","coreVersion":"10.303","createdTime":1690825120442,"modifiedTime":1690825120442,"lastModifiedBy":"kpZ1DNCgd1F5Mepo"},"_id":"0d1GSqt1ho1KMMas"}
{"type":"npc_class","name":"OPERATOR","img":"systems/lancer/assets/icons/npc_class.svg","system":{"lid":"npcc_operator","name":"OPERATOR","role":"artillery","info":{"flavor":"Operators are known-unknowns, rarely encountered on the front lines, but this should not be mistaken for fragility. Operators are dangerous and deadly in every way. Like their mechs, Operators’ bodies are loaded with the most advanced tech available. When they die in combat, it’s not unknown for their bodies – and their mechs — to self-immolate, rendering any technology and data into ash.","tactics":"Operators are elite and extremely mobile artillery mechs. They aren’t particularly hardy, but can use Trace Drive to teleport around the battlefield and put themselves in advantageous positions: on top of obstructions or terrain, or in cover – anywhere they can snipe at enemies with their highly accurate Raptor Plasma Rifles."},"power":100,"base_features":[{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_raptor_plasma_rifle_operator","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_trace_drive_operator","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_step_operator","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_self_erasure_operator","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"}],"optional_features":[{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_fade_generator_operator","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_telefrag_operator","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_fortress_operator","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_skirmisher_operator","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_nova_missiles_operator","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"}],"base_stats":{"activations":[1,1,1],"armor":[0,0,0],"hp":[10,12,15],"evade":[10,12,14],"edef":[10,12,14],"heatcap":[8,8,8],"speed":[5,5,5],"sensor":[10,10,10],"save":