{"type":"npc_class","name":"GOLIATH","img":"systems/lancer/assets/icons/npc_class.svg","system":{"lid":"npcc_goliath","name":"GOLIATH","role":"defender","info":{"flavor":"Along the Sierra Madre Line – the eighth ring of territory out from Cradle – the Dangun frame is a familiar sight. Manufactured by Park Armored Systems and popularized by the Dagger Squadron mercenary company, the Dangun is popular for its toughness, kinetic damage-trade ability, and reliable all-theater performance. The Dangun is a mech to build strike forces around – a Goliath-class frame capable of mounting powerful magtech, with a design that’s tough to counter in kinetic damage combat.<br>With a number of small fleet contracts in its portfolio, Park Armored Systems is a manufacturer worth keeping an eye on; indeed, Harrison Armory has taken particular notice, and omninet rumors suggest a possible partnership in the near future.","tactics":"Goliaths are relatively mobile defenders that can bring enemies to them. With Crush Targeting, Goliaths force dangerous enemies to focus attacks on them; all it needs is line of sight, allowing Goliaths to target even fast or hard-to-hit characters. The prodigious size of Goliaths also lets them provide cover for their allies."},"power":100,"base_features":[{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_drum_shotgun_goliath","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_crush_targeting_goliath","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_heavy_frame_goliath","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_guardian_goliath","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_siege_armor_goliath","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"}],"optional_features":[{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_power_knuckle_goliath","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_pin_goliath","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_crushing_embrace_goliath","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_watchful_guardian_goliath","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_retribution_goliath","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"}],"base_stats":{"activations":[1,1,1],"armor":[0,0,0],"hp":[25,30,35],"evade":[6,6,6],"edef":[6,6,6],"heatcap":[8,10,12],"speed":[3,3,3],"sensor":[10,10,15],"save":[11,13,15],"hull":[4,6,6],"agility":[-2,-2,-2],"systems":[1,1,1],"engineering":[0,0,2],"size":[[3],[3],[3]]}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"kpZ1DNCgd1F5Mepo":3},"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"lancer","systemVersion":"1.6.1","coreVersion":"10.303","createdTime":1690825120484,"modifiedTime":1690825120484,"lastModifiedBy":"kpZ1DNCgd1F5Mepo"},"_id":"KzIR1kf8nDXFgFpn"}
{"type":"npc_class","name":"AEGIS","img":"systems/lancer/assets/icons/npc_class.svg","system":{"lid":"npcc_aegis","name":"AEGIS","role":"support","info":{"flavor":"Aegis-archetype mechs are built to hold ground, support their allies, and suppress enemies. First used to great effect during the Comorrand Action by a Karrakin pilot, Lady Gloria of House MacLennan, Aegis’s are known for their powerful defensive measures. Their pilots can expertly make a bulwark out of the smallest barricade with anything from conventional tools to cutting-edge technologies.","tactics":"Aegises are tough and defensive support units. They are most effective when positioned so that their Defense Net can cover as many allies as possible since they can be difficult to redeploy. Regenerative Shielding also protects the Aegis from mobility-reducing effects."},"power":100,"base_features":[{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_light_laser_aegis","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_defense_net_aegis","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_regenerative_shielding_aegis","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"}],"optional_features":[{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_adaptive_shielding_aegis","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_guardian_aegis","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_ring_of_fire_aegis","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_hardlight_cover_system_aegis","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_ha_blackwall_system_aegis","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"}],"base_stats":{"activations":[1,1,1],"armor":[2,2,3],"hp":[14,18,18],"evade":[7,8,8],"edef":[10,12,14],"heatcap":[10,10,10],"speed":[3,3,3],"sensor":[8,10,10],"save":[10,11,12],"hull":[0,0,0],"agility":[-2,-1,-1],"systems":[2,3,4],"engineering":[2,3,5],"size":[[1],[1],[1]]}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"owner